  "Description": "The UseSettings goal attempts to access a specific setting and returns its value. It first logs a message indicating the attempt to access the setting. Then, it retrieves the value of the setting identified by %Settings.TestSettingsAskKey% and assigns it to the variable %myKey%. After that, it logs the value of %myKey% before returning this value.",
